c: 12
v: 68
t: "Mugihe binjira muri ico gihugu ca Misiri (Egypte) nkuko Se wabo yababwiye, ntaco vyabamariye imbere y’Imana atari ivyari kumutima wa Se wabo Yaa’qubu (iii) yashikanye, ntankeka uyo Se wabo Yaa’qubu (iii) yari afise ubumenyi kubera yuko twamwigishije, mugabo abantu benshi ntavyo bazi"